Author: SHossain#0007
Content:
A lot of you have requested to integrate exchange feature into Agama. We listened and happy to announce that buying and selling of some coins directly from Agama desktop (Lite mode) is now possible using Agama version 0.3.4. Thanks to our talented Agama developer @pbca26 for bringing us this exciting feature.  Please don't get confused with DEX. This is purely CEX (coinswitch.co API) integration into Agama. If you are interested and determined to try it out, please let me know, or ask in #deleted-channel channel.
Currently, these coins are available to trade using coinswitch API
```
Komodo, Bitcoin, Litecoin, Dash, Qtum, Digibyte, Bitcoin Gold, Dogecoin, GameCredits, Zcash, ZClassic, Vertcoin, Feathercoin, Namecoin, Myriad, SIBCoin, GoByte.
```
